Bugfixes and UX improvements
Community Submissions are here! Join us in celebrating the beauty of instant portraits and win Polaroid film. Available in the United States and mainland Europe
Bug fixes and UX improvements

iPhone 15 and iPhone 15 Pro support to expose photos with your Polaroid Lab! In this version we improved the look and feel of the I 2 section and improved app stability during long BULB exposures. Important Compatibility Update: Starting with this version our app will no longer run on iOS 14. Please update your phone to the latest iOS versions. We would like to extend our heartfelt thanks for your patience and support as we continue to improve the app.

Firmware update for your I 2 camera: Update firmware to ensure the best performance of your camera. You can now see the aperture and shutter speed values during long and bulb exposures with your I 2 camera. The Volume buttons setting is now disabled by default to avoid any accidental shots with your I 2 and Now cameras. You can turn this on in the Settings menu. Bugfixes and UX improvements

This version adds support for the Polaroid I 2. Designed for craft it s our first analog instant camera with built in manual controls and comes with the sharpest ever Polaroid lens. Made for the Imperfectionists.

This version adds support for the Polaroid I 2. Designed for craft it s our first analog instant camera with built in manual controls and comes with the sharpest ever Polaroid lens. Made for the Imperfectionists.

What s new in this version: We have added a convenient way that allows you to share scanned photos as Instagram stories. Please note this feature will roll out over the coming weeks. We have fixed the reported localization issues. Thank you for using our app!

Capture and share memories like never before with the latest version of the Polaroid app. In this release: We have improved the sharing editor: Enhance and share your Polaroid photos effortlessly with our improved editing tools. Tap on the share button on a scanned Polaroid photo to get started. We fixed a crash that happened when you tried to navigate to the Light Painting mode of the Now camera from the main screen. We fixed a bug where after editing a scanned Polaroid photo the next photo was not always displayed. Stay tuned for more exciting updates!

Express your creativity and share your photos in a truly memorable way with our latest update! Using our new stunning edit options with just a few taps you can now give your photos an artistic touch and make your memories even more vibrant. You can access this feature by tapping on the share button while viewing a scanned photo. Update today and bring your shared Polaroid photos to life!

Share your scanned Polaroid photos with friends and family in a new format when you tap on the share button Improved app start time for a faster and smoother user experience Updated privacy policy We appreciate your feedback and will continue to make updates to improve your experience with our app. Thank you for using our app!
Polaroid Lab now supports Reclaimed Edition Film

What s new in this version: Support for the new iPhone 13. Added option of selecting Round Frame in Polaroid Lab. Navigation improvements and other bug fixes.
This update includes a complete redesign of the home screen making your cameras scanner and Polaroid Lab easier to access. We also added in extra creative tools for the new Polaroid Now camera.

Thank you for using the Polaroid Originals app. We continuously improve our app and fix bugs. In this release among other things we extended compatibility to iOS 12.
New in this update: Under the hood improvements that improve stability of the app when viewing AR photos

New in this update: Dark mode has arrived: the app will follow the settings from your phone and switch to a dark background. Your eyes will get some relief in dark mode. Duochrome film selection is now available for Polaroid Lab. We optimized the color quality for prints on the Polaroid Lab
This update contains an important update for Polaroid Lab: Compatibility for new phones on the Polaroid Lab for photo exposures
Bug fixes and improvements.

A new inspiration screen has been added showing tips tricks and useful information about our cameras and film. We will update this section frequently. Major improvements to how large images are processed when exposing on the lab making the process much faster. Improvements to black and white exposures allowing for more mid tones when exposing onto black and white film.

Share your collages created for Polaroid with your friends and family. Major improvements to the quality of collages on Polaroid Lab. Improved speed of navigating trough different collages. Preview your AR media in the Lab gallery by pressing on an AR photo.
This release contains a minor fix for storing the Polaroid Lab manually adjusted exposure settings after closing the app.
What s new in this update: The Polaroid Lab now works with the new iPhone SE We are constantly working on improving the app please let us know about your experience! Stay safe and healthy!

The Polaroid Originals app is now part of the unified Polaroid brand! In this update: new design elements reflecting the new Polaroid brand optimization of colour quality of photos on the Polaroid Lab for iPhone LCD screens improvements to the barcode for better AR scanning results under the hood fixes for bugs and crashes

In this update we bring you some fixes to improve the Polaroid Originals app experience: improved quality for scanning Polaroid photos improved error handling when viewing AR photos smoother content loading in the Inspiration section a few app crashes were fixed for better app stability

New improvements in this update: Making a scan of coloured and patterned Polaroid frames with the Scanner is now much better! We improved the quality of photos printed on the Polaroid app for iPhones with OLED screens The alignment of photo s printed of the Lab is more accurate We optimised the performance and app stability of the app with Polaroid Lab More improvements are on the way. Keep sharing meaningful memories on your Polaroid pictures!

We added additional languages in the Polaroid Originals app: Italian German and Spanish. Fixed several issues when exposing photo s on the Polaroid Lab for increased performance and incorrect exposures.
In this version we optimized the Polaroid Lab features: several crashes were fixed improved performance for AR upload and recognition scaling of video has been optimized

Transform your digital photos into real Polaroid pictures using the Polaroid Originals app. Turn a digital photo on your phone into a single Polaroid picture on the Polaroid Lab. Create a collage of two three four six or nine frames. For iPhones that support AR: Embed a video or second image into your Polaroid picture using our AR feature View your AR photos to watch your memories or your friend s come to life

New in the Polaroid Originals app: Fixed an issue where the address field was hidden when sending feedback or sharing a scanned Polaroid. Scanning for colored polaroid frames has been optimized. Please let us know if you have any feedback on how to improve your app experience!

New in the Polaroid Originals app: Portrait Mode is a completely new mode for the OneStep to shoot beautiful portraits. The My Photos section has a new overview and improved edit features. Support of the latest OneStep model Further bugfixes and stability improvements

New in the Polaroid Originals app: Portrait Mode is a completely new mode for the OneStep to shoot beautiful portraits. The My Photos section has a new overview and improved edit features. Support of the latest OneStep model Further bugfixes and stability improvements

What s new in the Polaroid Originals app: The volume buttons of your phone now work as a remote shutter button for the OneStep camera. You can now turn off the flash in all camera modes. The scanner supports Spectra format. Share your scanned photos directly in My Photos. Camera connections are now more reliable and stable. Further bugfixes and stability improvements
We continually improve the Polaroid Originals app. Keep your updates turned on so you never miss a new feature! This version contains stability improvements and performance optimizations.
